 style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><b><i><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ranveer_Singh" target="_blank">Ranveer Singh</a></i></b></span>. You will see her sporting in amazing gadwals, tanchoi, matka cotton to amazing Gujrati stitch collections.<br><br>Check the Instagram post here, where Falguni is matching steps with Ranveer- <span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><b><i><u>https://www.instagram.com/p/BBakj67KuiF/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</u></i></b></span></span></p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-3-1678215407152.png?v=1678215409" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-3-1678215407152.png?v=1678215409 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-3-1678215407152_500x.png?v=1678215409 320w" width="1200" height="628" style="aspect-ratio:1200 / 628" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-nVkyK eXnudJ pf-88_"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-51_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-52_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-53_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-55_"><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><b><i><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soma_Mondal" target="_blank">Soma Mondal, Chairperson of SAIL - (Steel Authority of India Limited)</a></i></b></span></span></h3><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-56_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-58_">Well, particularly the Iron lady of India in 2023 - Soma Mondal became the first woman to chair the state-run Steel Authority of India (SAIL) in January 2021.<br><br>She has led the steelmaker to record financial growth since taking over: the company's profits surged surged threefold to 120 billion rupees in her first year at the helm.Mondal first became a director for the company in 2017. She's responsible for launching an 80,000-million-rupee effort to expand production capacity.<br><br>She has more than three decades of experience in the metals industry. After graduating from college with a degree in electrical engineering, she joined state-run National Aluminium Co.<br><br>The lady has loved her drape since a long time - from her office to the various SAIL events we have seen her wearing ikat, raw silk with large temple border to jamdani of various fusion and traditional style.  </span></p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-4-1678215526464.png?v=1678215528" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-4-1678215526464.png?v=1678215528 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/54/assets/pastel-pink-minimalist-business-blogger-facebook-ad-4-1678215526464_500x.png?v=1678215528 320w" width="1200" height="628" style="aspect-ratio:1200 / 628" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-nVkyK eXnudJ pf-50_"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-59_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-61_"><br><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Priyanka_Chopra" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><i><b>Priyanka Chopra Jonas - Actor, Producer, Forbes 100 Most Infleuntial Women of 2022</b></i></span></a></span></h3><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-62_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-64_">The Miss World 2000 is now one of the highest-paid actress in India who bagged tow national Film Awards, 5 Filmfare Awards and honored with Padmashri, is also in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forbes" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><i><b>Forbes</b></i></span></a> list of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forbes_list_of_The_World%27s_100_Most_Powerful_Women" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><b><i>World's 100 Most Powerful Women</i></b></span></a>. She has made an incredible journey from Bollywood to Hollywood and not just in movies she is currently one of the most successful entrepreneur.<br><br>Chopra's other ventures include tech investments, a haircare brand, a restaurant, and a homeware line. She promotes social causes such as environment and women's rights and is vocal about gender equality, the gender pay gap, and feminism. She has worked with UNICEF since 2006 and was appointed as the national and global UNICEF Goodwill Ambassador for child rights in 2010 and 2016. On Instagram, Chopra is the most followed Indian actor.<br><br>You can see her sporting all the Bollywood Diva style whenever she is sporting herself in a saree - from georgette to sequin, Parsi embroidery to the linen of classic material - she has tried out and mingled the wardrobe with great elegance.  </span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-65_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-67_"><i><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CbgjakhLNYI/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link" target="_blank"><u><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">Check Priyanka's&nbsp;Instagram channel</span></b></u></a></i></span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-68_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-70_"><i>Women are considered more emotional than men, but successful woman leaders in India are those who are extremely resilient in their work. Even if problems or difficulties come, women leaders need to fight to get up and stay resilient in what they do.<br><br>These people whom I mentioned above, are hugely celebrated and they are the true form of the Naari’s of 2023. And observe, the saree makes every woman differently elegant and poised. All of the women mentioned in my blog today have worn sarees which are quite common to IndyVogue and trust me you can style like too and bring out your own elegance to match the step of beauty with grace and brains. </i></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-72_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-74_"><br>Author's Bio</span></h3><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-75_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-77_">Sumana Bhattacharya completed her Masters in Economics from the University of Calcutta &amp; was working with the Department of Education, Govt. of West Bengal to provide training to the teachers in Government Schools. She moved to USA in 2005 after getting married &amp; is the mother of 2 kids. She is the one that drives IndyVogue every day, every hour, every minute and every second. Salute to her and her undying spirit.</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-78_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-80_"><br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
